app_name: Groups Control Groups Photo and Video Editing Apps Video Speed Editor Slow Fast
app_description: Easiest Video Speed Editor!! First divide your video into multiple short clips that need different speeds. Set the speed for each short clip review. You can set up to 8x slow or fast motion speeds. Merge all the short clips back to one. That s it ! You can apply various overlay shapes and filter effects for each short clip before merging. Add beautiful background music from the app library or from your iPod library. Or keep original audio as it is. Have fun with the speed!!
